operationName: client transaction from start to end

modal.businessField:
select
region_id as METRICID,
count(1) as CALLCOUNT,LONGSUM(network_time) as NETWORK,
LONGSUM(web_time)
as WEB,LONGSUM(page_time) as PAGE,
LONGSUM(dom_time) as
DOM,LONGSUM(queue_time) as QUEUE,
LONGSUM(extra_time) as
EXTRA,LONGSUM(app_time) as APP,
LONGSUM(all_time) as
ALLTIME,LONGSUM(apdex_sat) as
APDEXSAT,
LONGSUM(apdex_tol) as
APDEXTOL,
LONGSUM(apdex_fru) as APDEXFRU,
DOUBLEMAX(apdex_t) as
APDEXT,LONGSUM(domloading_time) as
DOMLOADINGTIME,
LONGSUM(domcontentloadedevent_start_time) as
DOMCONTENTLOADEDEVENTSTART,
LONGSUM(loadevent_start_time) as
LOADEVENTSTART,LONGSUM(feel_time) as
FEELTIME
from
bi_rum_metrics
WHERE timestamp between 1480920540000 and 1480922340000
and user_id=?
and application_id=? 
group by region_id
limit 500 break by 1480920540000 to 1800000
